  <num>49-308</num>
  <heading>Appointments to grade of 2nd lieutenant.</heading>
  <text>All appointments to the grade of 2nd lieutenant shall be from the enlisted men, under regulations prescribed by the Commanding General, and subject to the examination required by law.</text>
